{"type": "article", "id": 25246, "title": "带有科幻色彩的餐具", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-11T06:59:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115104KDHsNIgRb59nVulS.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组餐具系列都带有一些好玩的科幻色彩，来自意大利家居品牌 Diesel Living 和意大利设计品牌 Seletti。餐盘的图案来自星球，而胡椒瓶则是一艘火箭，白色瓷盘的边缘是齿轮的形状，点缀以金属色提亮，在奇幻中富有想象力。这套餐具将和之前的系列一起在 2016 年米兰家居展上展出，<a href=\"http://store.diesel.com/magazine/en/living-category/home-accessories/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115101KXesaCoYjpHTZur9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115102jQovZ23twKqS70IT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70870871\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115103yfLgUlQx0orjKaIP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115103PlNEHMDkOTR0SmWo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}